1gksu -u user_name chromium
can run chromium in the root
but the extensions can not be installed
2)can export CHROMIUM_FLAGS='--enable-remote-extensions'
also can run this with shell then can use the extensions
can write into the /etc/profile
3)the flash player in the chromium problem
pepper flash to install in the dir of the plugin in chromium
download the pepper flash and unzip into the /usr/lib/chromium/plugins
then add the path to the CHROMIUM_FLAGS
--ppapi-flash-path=/usr/lib/chromium/plugins/libpepflashplayer.so



